message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with the application of deep convolutional neural networks for the detection of lymph nodes in CT scans. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper has direct applications in the medical field (cs.MED) and utilizes neural networks (cs.NEURON) as a key component of the proposed method.
